{"tid":1464683,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［身體力行有圖］你今日唱左未？","createTime":"2019-08-13T15:20:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T15:20:12.000Z","uid":164325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9831880236527ae0deb1c86292b8ef0fb1f87b27","tid":1464683,"uid":164325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:20:12.000Z","msg":"借acc<br />\n少少地，聽日去唱美金。唔好得個講字，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要快過班藍絲，等佢哋套唔到現。</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今日隔黎櫃檯已經有好多師奶已經大量拎緊外幣。<br />\n問咗恒X銀行， ATM㩒外幣係冇手續費㗎 ！匯率係同去分行唱一樣。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iUGcUT4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiUGcUT4.jpg&h=9f59ee64&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外附送簡易開外國戶口攻略：<br />\n（前提你要有一百萬港元）<br />\n簡單來講就係喺香港匯豐開一個卓越理財戶口，入場費一百萬存款，然後就可以免費開一個海外戶口。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190813/59927805\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190813%2F59927805&d=GlETU%2Fuc5qoZzc1QHf9C2uu9cyR3gY7uP1sO3WVLDIg%3D&h=915f3339\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190813%2F59927805&h=6f3cac3d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190813/59927805</a>"}]}